OL,3,CCheshire man jailed after conning
OL,4,Cblind piano tuner out thousands of
OL,5,Cpounds
OL,7,FA fraudster from Macclesfield has been
OL,8,Fjailed for conning a blind piano tuner
OL,9,Fout of a hundred and eighty five
OL,10,Fthousand pounds after a four year scam.
OL,12,FMark Stanner, who is 42 and of of
OL,13,FBrocklehurst Avenue in Macclesfield,
OL,14,Fused a call centre company in
OL,15,FManchester as a front to bombard the
OL,16,Fvictim, a man in his 50s, with phone
OL,17,Fcalls, texts and emails.
