OL,3,CCheshire man jailed after conning
OL,4,Cblind piano tuner out thousands of
OL,5,Cpounds
OL,7,FThe victim was told that he owed money
OL,8,Fto various publication companies for
OL,9,Fadverts that had been placed in
OL,10,Fnumerous publications to advertise his
OL,11,Ftrade as a piano tuner.
OL,13,FTo begin with the financial demands
OL,14,Fwere small, dating back to 2017.
OL,16,FThe victim paid the initial demands,
OL,17,Frequesting that Stanner would leave
OL,18,Fhim alone if he paid. As time went on,
OL,19,Fthese demands progressively got more
OL,20,Fand more aggressive and frequent.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
