OL,7,FOfficers investigating the scam
OL,8,Fdiscovered that Stanner was using the
OL,9,Fmoney to fund his gambling habit.
OL,11,FAlongside Stanner 41-year-old Marvin
OL,12,FScott of Charlestown Road, Manchester
OL,13,Fwas jailed for 31 months after he
OL,14,Fallowed #48,000 from the company to
OL,15,Fmove through his bank accounts to
OL,16,Fconceal the finances for Stanner.
