OL,7,FDetective Constable Michelle
OL,8,FWilkinson, of GMP's Economic Crime
OL,9,FTeam, said: "Stanner has shown no
OL,10,Fremorse throughout our investigation
OL,11,Fand has actively sought to conceal his
OL,12,Ffinances by enlisting the help of
OL,13,FTurner and Scott who kept money in
OL,14,Ftheir accounts for Stanner.
