OL,7,F"Sadly, this case demonstrates how
OL,8,Feasy it is for people to fall victim
OL,9,Fto fraudsters, especially when they
OL,10,Fare convincing. The victim was
OL,11,Fvulnerable, and Stanner took advantage
OL,12,Fof this. I hope he spends his time in
OL,13,Fjail thinking about the consequences
OL,14,Fof his actions.
