OL,7,F"We would like to use this opportunity
OL,8,Fto ensure that we are providing crime
OL,9,Fprevention advice to individuals
OL,10,Facross Greater Manchester, we want to
OL,11,Fequip our communities with advice on
OL,12,Fhow to reduce your chances of falling
OL,13,Fvictim to fraud.
OL,15,F"Look out for unexpected contact from
OL,16,Funknown companies asking for your
OL,17,Fmoney, the likelihood is that this is
OL,18,Ffraudulent.
