OL,3,CCheshire man jailed after conning
OL,4,Cblind piano tuner out thousands of
OL,5,Cpounds
OL,7,F"With cases like this, it is common
OL,8,Fthere is no written invoice prior to
OL,9,Fthe payment just a demand for money
OL,10,Fwith little to no explanation of why
OL,11,Fthey need to be paid.
OL,13,F"Fraudsters will often say that the
OL,14,Fpayment is urgent and will accompany
OL,15,Fthe demand for money with immediate
OL,16,Fthreats of bailiffs and debt
OL,17,Fcollectors, putting pressure on
OL,18,Fvictim's to part with their money.
